:wiggins a ex:FictionalPerson ;
    ex:lastName "Wiggins" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Wiggins" ;
    ex:description "Wiggins is the leader and spokesman of the Baker Street Irregulars, Holmes's street Arab detective corps. A young boy who reports to Holmes at 221B Baker Street. Found Jefferson Hope's cab. In The Sign of the Four, Wiggins leads the Baker Street Irregulars in searching the Thames for the steam launch Aurora. Taller and older than the other boys, with an air of lounging superiority. Holmes's dirty little lieutenant." ;
    ex:knows :sherlockHolmes ;
    ex:leaderOf :bakerStreetIrregulars ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
    dc:source :signOfTheFourDoc ;
    dc:source :studyInScarletDoc ;
    dc:source :illustriousClientDoc .


