:bludgeonAttacker a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Criminal ;
    ex:prefLabel "Bludgeon Attacker" ;
    skos:altLabel "the rough" ;
    ex:description "An unnamed rough who attacked Sherlock Holmes with a bludgeon on Holmes's way to Watson's house on the evening of April 24th. Holmes knocked him down and the police arrested him. Holmes stated with absolute confidence that no connection would ever be traced between this man and Professor Moriarty." ;
    ex:hasParticipantIn :bludgeonAttackOnHolmes ;
