    ex:description "Carrie Evans, also known as Mrs. Norlett under her married name, is Lady Beatrice Falder's confidential maid for five years. Her maiden name is Evans. She is described as a highly coloured young woman with flaxen hair and impudent eyes. There is an implied affair between her and Sir Robert Norberton. She is a willing participant in the scheme to conceal Lady Beatrice's death, serving as Sir Robert's confidante and tool in the deception." ;
    ex:occupation "lady's maid" ;
