    ex:description "A retired military officer and old friend of Dr. Watson, who had come under Watson's professional care in Afghanistan. A fine old soldier who had seen much of the world. He took a bachelor house near Reigate in Surrey and invited Watson and Holmes to stay. He owns a collection of Eastern weapons kept in a gun-room. He participated in the investigation at the Cunningham house." ;
    ex:occupation "retired military officer" ;
