:coramSecondSecretary a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Detective ;
    ex:prefLabel "Professor Coram's Second Secretary" ;
    ex:description "Unnamed man who served as Professor Coram's second secretary. Actually an agent from a private detective firm hired by Anna to infiltrate the household. Found that papers were kept in the bureau cupboard, obtained an impression of the Chubb's key, furnished Anna with a plan of the house, and informed her that the study was empty in the forenoon. Left hurriedly before Anna's own attempt to retrieve the papers." ;
    ex:occupation "private detective, secretary (cover)" ;
    ex:employedBy :professorCoram ;
