:countessDAlbert a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Victim ;
    ex:lastName "d'Albert" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Countess d'Albert" ;
    ex:description "A countess mentioned in the context of Milverton's late-night meeting. The woman posing as a treacherous maid claims to have five letters compromising the Countess d'Albert, which she offers to sell to Milverton. This is part of the avenger's ruse to gain access to Milverton." ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
    dc:source :milvertonDoc .

:countNegrettoSylvius a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Criminal ;
    ex:firstName "Negretto" ;
    ex:lastName "Sylvius" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Count Negretto Sylvius" ;
    skos:altLabel "Count Sylvius" ;
    skos:altLabel "Sylvius" ;
    ex:description "Count Negretto Sylvius is a half-Italian criminal, a famous game-shot, sportsman, and man-about-town. He is big and swarthy with a formidable dark moustache shading a cruel thin-lipped mouth, surmounted by a long curved nose like the beak of an eagle. He dresses well but flamboyantly with a brilliant necktie, shining pin, and glittering rings. He lives at 136 Moorside Gardens, N.W. He used to shoot lions in Algeria. He stole the Crown diamond (Mazarin Stone) from Whitehall with Sam Merton. Holmes's notebook records his involvement in the death of old Mrs. Harold (who left him the Blymer estate which he rapidly gambled away), the complete life history of Miss Minnie Warrender, a robbery on the train de-luxe to the Riviera on February 13 1892, and a forged check on the Credit Lyonnais in the same year. He carries a revolver and a loaded cane. He is described as having Southern graces of manner when in the mood but being a devil incarnate in the other mood. Holmes calls him a shark and a master criminal." ;
    ex:title "Count" ;
    ex:occupation "sportsman, game-shot" ;
    ex:livesAt :136MoorsideGardens ;
    ex:owns :sylviusRevolver ;
    ex:owns :sylviusCane ;
    ex:confederateOf :samMerton ;
    ex:arrestedIn :arrestOfSylviusAndMerton ;
    ex:knows :samMerton ;
    ex:knows :ikeySanders ;
    ex:knows :vanSeddar ;
    ex:knows :straubenzee ;
    ex:hasParticipantIn :theftOfMazarinStone ;
    ex:hasParticipantIn :arrestOfSylviusAndMerton ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
