:steveDixie a ex:FictionalPerson , ex:Criminal ;
    ex:firstName "Steve" ;
    ex:lastName "Dixie" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Steve Dixie" ;
    skos:altLabel "Black Steve" ;
    ex:description "A large Black prizefighter and bruiser, member of the Spencer John gang. Sent by Barney Stockdale to threaten Sherlock Holmes into staying away from the Harrow Weald case. Wore a loud gray check suit with a salmon-coloured tie. Connected to the killing of young Perkins outside the Holborn Bar. Claimed to have been training at the Bull Ring in Birmingham at the time. Lurked outside The Three Gables to keep watch. Easily cowed by Holmes despite his intimidating appearance." ;
    ex:occupation "prizefighter" ;
    ex:employedBy :barneyStockdale ;
