:susanStockdale a ex:FictionalPerson , ex:Criminal , ex:Servant ;
    ex:firstName "Susan" ;
    ex:lastName "Stockdale" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Susan Stockdale" ;
    skos:altLabel "Susan" ;
    ex:description "Maid and servant at The Three Gables, secretly the wife of Barney Stockdale. Planted by Isadora Klein as an inside agent. A great gaunt woman, wheezy. Eavesdropped on Holmes's conversation with Mrs. Maberley. Communicated with Barney Stockdale over the garden hedge, passing on information that Mrs. Maberley had written to Holmes. Quit her position after Holmes confronted her. Planned the entrance used by the burglars." ;
    ex:occupation "servant" ;
    ex:employedBy :maryMaberley , :isadoraKlein ;
    ex:isMarriedTo :barneyStockdale ;
    ex:knows :barneyStockdale , :isadoraKlein ;
