    ex:description "An unnamed woman employed by Forbes to shadow Mrs. Tangey. She was with Mrs. Tangey twice when she was drunk but could get nothing out of her regarding the stolen treaty." ;
    ex:employedBy :scotlandYard ;
    ex:knows :mrsTangey ;
