:georgeTregennis a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Victim ;
    ex:firstName "George" ;
    ex:lastName "Tregennis" ;
    ex:prefLabel "George Tregennis" ;
    ex:description "Elder brother of the Tregennis siblings. Lived at Tredannick Wartha with his brother Owen and sister Brenda. Was Mortimer's partner at whist on the night of the poisoning. Noticed something moving in the garden bushes during the card game. Driven insane by devil's-foot root poison placed in the fire by Mortimer, found laughing, shouting, and singing with an expression of utmost horror. Taken to the asylum at Helston." ;
    ex:livesAt :tredannickWartha ;
