:jonasOldacre a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Criminal ;
    ex:firstName "Jonas" ;
    ex:lastName "Oldacre" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Jonas Oldacre" ;
    ex:description "Builder of Lower Norwood, 82 years described as 'not old' so likely middle-aged. Known as a malicious, vindictive man with a cruel streak from boyhood (set a cat on fire). Former sweetheart of Mrs. McFarlane, who broke off their engagement upon discovering his cruelty. Faked his own murder to frame John Hector McFarlane as revenge against Mrs. McFarlane. Hid in a secret room behind a lath-and-plaster partition at Deep Dene House. Used alias 'Mr. Cornelius' for fraudulent banking. Planted McFarlane's thumbprint in blood on the wall. Conspired with housekeeper Mrs. Lexington." ;
    ex:occupation "builder" ;
    ex:hasAlias "Mr. Cornelius" ;
