    ex:prefLabel "Jose" ;
    ex:description "Garcia's faithful manservant and countryman at Wisteria Lodge. A melancholy, swarthy individual. Could speak English and did the housekeeping. Delivered the note that lured Garcia to his death. One of Garcia's two companions of humble station in the revenge plot. Fled the house on the night of the murder." ;
    ex:occupation "manservant" ;
