    ex:lastName "Vibart" ;
    skos:altLabel "Jules" ;
    ex:description "Jules Vibart is a head waiter at the Hotel National in Lausanne and the lover and fiancé of Marie Devine. He connected Lady Frances Carfax's sudden departure from the hotel with the visit of a tall, dark, bearded man (Philip Green), whom he described as 'un sauvage'. He refused to discuss why Marie had left Lady Frances's service." ;
    ex:occupation "head waiter" ;
    ex:knows :marieDevine, :ladyFrancesCarfax ;
