    ex:prefLabel "Le Brun" ;
    ex:description """Le Brun is a French agent who was beaten by Apaches in the Montmartre district of Paris and crippled for life. He had been inquiring into Baron Gruner's affairs only a week before the attack. Baron Gruner references his fate as a veiled threat to Holmes.""" ;
