    ex:description "Mrs. Harold is an old woman whose death is recorded in Holmes's notebook as one of Count Negretto Sylvius's crimes. She left Sylvius the Blymer estate, which he rapidly gambled away. The implication is that her death was suspicious or criminal." ;
