    ex:lastName "Lexington" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Mrs. Lexington" ;
    ex:description "Housekeeper to Jonas Oldacre at Deep Dene House. Complicit in Oldacre's scheme to fake his murder. An old woman, described as of respectable appearance. Knew Oldacre was hiding in the secret room and likely provided him food." ;
