    ex:prefLabel "Mrs. Marker" ;
    ex:description "Elderly, sad-faced housekeeper at Yoxley Old Place. Has been with Professor Coram since his arrival. Confirmed Professor was in night-clothes at time of murder. Had been tidying the study about a quarter of an hour before the crime. Confirmed she dusted the bureau the previous morning and the scratch was not present then." ;
    ex:occupation "housekeeper" ;
    ex:livesAt :yoxleyOldPlace ;
