:mrsMcFarlaneNorwood a ex:FictionalPerson ;
    ex:lastName "McFarlane" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Mrs. McFarlane" ;
    ex:description "Mother of John Hector McFarlane. Lives at Torrington Lodge, Blackheath. Was formerly engaged to Jonas Oldacre but broke off the engagement upon discovering his cruel and malicious nature. Oldacre's scheme to frame her son was motivated by revenge for this rejection. Her photograph was found in Oldacre's possessions, defaced with a knife." ;
    ex:formerPartnerOf :jonasOldacre ;
