    ex:description "Wife of Captain Peter Carey. A haggard, grey-haired woman with a gaunt and deep-lined face and a furtive look of terror in her red-rimmed eyes, showing years of hardship and ill-usage. Identified the sheath-knife found at the crime scene as her husband's property." ;
    ex:isMarriedTo :peterCarey ;
    ex:parentOf :missPeterCarey ;
