:mrsPorter a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Servant ;
    ex:lastName "Porter" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Mrs. Porter" ;
    ex:description "The old Cornish cook and housekeeper at Tredannick Wartha. With the aid of a young girl, looked after the wants of the Tregennis family. Slept deeply on the night of the poisoning and heard no sound. Fainted with horror upon entering the room in the morning and finding the victims. After recovering, she opened the window and sent a farm-lad for the doctor. Was leaving Tredannick Wartha that afternoon to rejoin her family at St. Ives." ;
    ex:occupation "cook, housekeeper" ;
    ex:employedBy :tredannickWartha ;
