    ex:prefLabel "Mrs. Pringle" ;
    ex:description "Elderly housekeeper to Eduardo Lucas at 16 Godolphin Street. Retires early and sleeps at the top of the house. Heard nothing on the night of the crime. If her master had a visitor he had himself admitted him. Corroborated that items found in Mitton's boxes were presents from Lucas." ;
    ex:occupation "housekeeper" ;
    ex:livesAt :16GodolphinStreet ;
