    ex:description "An unnamed faithful friend of the Neligan family who was a business man. He discovered some time after the failure of Dawson and Neligan that some of the securities Neligan Senior had taken with him had reappeared on the London market, setting young Neligan on the trail to Peter Carey." ;
    ex:occupation "business man" ;
    ex:knows :johnNeligan ;
