    ex:prefLabel "Poultney Square Sergeant" ;
    ex:description "An unnamed police sergeant who responded to Annie Fraser's call for police at 36 Poultney Square. He recognized Holmes by name and reputation but required him to leave without a warrant. He later volunteered to keep watch on the house and reported flickering lights in the windows near midnight." ;
