:ralphWife a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Servant ;
    ex:prefLabel "Ralph's Wife" ;
    ex:description "Ralph's wife is the wife of Ralph the butler at Tuxbury Old Park. She had been Godfrey Emsworth's nurse and was described as possibly older than her husband. Godfrey spoke of her as second only to his mother in his affections. Her name is not given in the text." ;
    ex:occupation "nurse, housekeeper" ;
