    ex:prefLabel "Bathsheba" ;
    ex:description "Biblical figure referenced by Holmes in connection with King David and Uriah. In the parallel to the Barclay case, Bathsheba corresponds to Nancy Devoy, the woman desired by both the betrayer and the betrayed." ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
