    ex:lastName "Cartwright" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Cartwright" ;
    ex:description "A member of the Worthingdon bank gang who participated in the 1875 bank robbery. He was hanged after Sutton/Blessington turned informer and gave evidence against him. His death was the motive for the other gang members' revenge against Sutton." ;
