    ex:description "A smart-looking police inspector who investigated Blessington's death at 403 Brook Street. He initially believed it was suicide but was persuaded by Holmes's deduction that it was murder. He took notes in a pocket-book and later arrested the page boy confederate." ;
    ex:occupation "police inspector" ;
    ex:knows :sherlockHolmes ;
