    ex:prefLabel "Thor Place Gamekeeper" ;
    ex:description "An unnamed gamekeeper at Thor Place who found Mrs. Gibson's body at approximately eleven o'clock at night at Thor Bridge. The body was then examined by police and a doctor before being carried to the house." ;
