    ex:description "The coachman who drove Dr. Trevelyan's brougham. Trevelyan asked Holmes if he had spoken to the coachman, but Holmes had deduced the waiting time from the candle instead." ;
    ex:occupation "coachman" ;
    ex:employedBy :percyTrevelyan ;
