:trevelyanPageBoy a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Page, ex:Accomplice ;
    ex:prefLabel "Trevelyan's page boy" ;
    ex:description "A young boy recently employed at Dr. Trevelyan's practice at 403 Brook Street. He admitted patients and waited downstairs. He was a confederate of Blessington's murderers, admitting them to the house and barring the door after them. He disappeared after the murder. Proceedings against him broke down for want of evidence." ;
    ex:workedAt :403BrookStreet ;
    ex:hasParticipantIn :murderOfBlessington ;
