    ex:description "The unnamed innkeeper at the village near Tuxbury Old Park. When James Dodd inquired about Godfrey Emsworth, the innkeeper confirmed the story that Godfrey had gone for a voyage round the world." ;
    ex:occupation "innkeeper" ;
