    ex:lastName "Westbury" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Violet Westbury" ;
    skos:altLabel "Miss Westbury" ;
    skos:altLabel "Miss Violet Westbury" ;
    ex:description "Fiancee of Arthur Cadogan West. A white-faced young lady. Last person to see West alive on Monday evening about 7:30pm when he left her abruptly in the fog without explanation. Wedding planned for New Year. Reports that West had been thoughtful and worried for the last week about something concerned with his official life, and had spoken of the importance of state secrets and the ease with which a traitor could obtain them. Found at Mrs. Cadogan West's house when Holmes visited." ;
