    ex:description "Scullery maid at Baskerville Hall, one of only two women in the house according to Barrymore. Sleeps in the other wing from the Barrymores. Her name is not given in the text." ;
    ex:occupation "scullery maid" ;
    ex:livesAt :baskervilleHall ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
