    ex:description "Unnamed clergyman who performed the secret marriage of Hatty Doran and Francis Hay Moulton in 1884 at McQuire's camp near the Rockies. Had been arranged in advance by Frank - described as 'a clergyman all ready in waiting.'" ;
    ex:occupation "Clergyman" ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
