:clotildeLothmanVonSaxeMeningen a ex:FictionalPerson ;
    ex:firstName "Clotilde" ;
    ex:lastName "Lothman von Saxe-Meningen" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Clotilde Lothman von Saxe-Meningen" ;
    ex:description "Clotilde Lothman von Saxe-Meningen is the second daughter of the King of Scandinavia. Betrothed to the King of Bohemia. Her family has strict principles. She is described as the very soul of delicacy. A shadow of doubt as to the King's conduct would end the betrothal." ;
    ex:betrothedTo :wilhelmVonOrmstein ;
    ex:childOf :kingOfScandinavia ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
