    ex:description "Housekeeper at Baskerville Hall and wife of John Barrymore. Born Eliza Selden; Selden the Notting Hill murderer is her younger brother. Large, impassive, heavy-featured woman with a stern expression. Wept bitterly at night over her brother's plight. Received 500 pounds in Sir Charles's will. Helped her brother by arranging food signals. Revealed the secret of the candle signal when confronted by Sir Henry." ;
    ex:occupation "housekeeper" ;
    ex:employedBy :henryBaskerville ;
