    ex:description "Young and singularly beautiful daughter of Jacob Shafter. German type, blonde and fair-haired with beautiful dark eyes. About nineteen years old. Falls in love with McMurdo despite being courted by Ted Baldwin. Married Edwards/McMurdo in Chicago after the Scowrer trial. Later died in California, making Douglas a widower before his second marriage to Ivy." ;
    ex:childOf :jacobShafter ;
