:evansConvict a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Convict, ex:Forger ;
    ex:lastName "Evans" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Evans" ;
    ex:description "A young fellow convict on the Gloria Scott, Armitage's neighbor on the other side from Prendergast. His crime was forgery. In much the same position as Armitage. Ready to join the mutiny conspiracy as the only means of saving himself. After the Gloria Scott's destruction, was among the dissenters picked up by the brig Hotspur. Changed his name (like Armitage) after landing at Sydney, went to the gold diggings, and became a rich and prosperous man in the south of England. One of the most educated of the boat party, helped work out their position after being set adrift." ;
    ex:occupation "Forger (former); rich colonial landowner" ;
    ex:knows :jamesArmitage ;
