    ex:lastName "Flaubert" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Gustave Flaubert" ;
    ex:description "Gustave Flaubert is a real historical figure, a French novelist. Holmes quotes his line 'L'homme c'est rien—l'oeuvre c'est tout' as written by Flaubert to George Sand, in the closing lines of The Red-Headed League." ;
