    skos:altLabel "Sergeant Holder" ;
    ex:description "John Holder is a company sergeant in the 3rd Buffs. One of the finest swimmers in the service. Saved Jonathan Small from drowning after a crocodile took his right leg in the Ganges." ;
    ex:gender "male" ;
