    ex:description "The unnamed mother of the child Lucy. She died of hunger and thirst during the desert crossing before John Ferrier and Lucy were found by the Mormon caravan." ;
    ex:causeOfDeath "died of thirst and hunger in the desert" ;
    ex:parentOf :lucyFerrier ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
    dc:source :studyInScarletDoc .

:lysanderStark a ex:FictionalPerson, ex:Criminal ;
    ex:firstName "Fritz" ;
    ex:lastName "Stark" ;
    ex:title "Colonel" ;
    ex:prefLabel "Colonel Lysander Stark" ;
    skos:altLabel "Colonel Stark" ;
    skos:altLabel "Fritz" ;
    ex:description "A man posing as a colonel with a German accent who hired Victor Hatherley to examine a hydraulic press near Eyford. His real first name is Fritz, revealed when Elise called out to him. He was rather over middle size but exceedingly thin, with a face sharpened into nose and chin, skin drawn tense over outstanding bones, bright eyes, and grey eyes. Nearer forty than thirty. He was the leader of a counterfeiting gang producing fraudulent half-crowns using a hydraulic press at Dr. Becher's house. He attempted to murder Hatherley by crushing him in the press, and when that failed, cut off Hatherley's thumb with a butcher's cleaver as he escaped. He was staying at Dr. Becher's house as a supposed patient. Holmes implied he had previously murdered Jeremiah Hayling, another hydraulic engineer. He escaped before police arrived, fleeing in a cart toward Reading with Elise and Ferguson." ;
    ex:occupation "counterfeiter" ;
    ex:age "nearer forty than thirty" ;
    ex:nationality "German" ;
    ex:alias "Colonel Lysander Stark" ;
    ex:hasPhysicalDescription "Rather over middle size but exceedingly thin, with whole face sharpened into nose and chin, skin drawn tense over outstanding bones; bright eyes, grey eyes; brisk step; plainly but neatly dressed." ;
    ex:leaderOf :starkCounterfeitingGang ;
    ex:livesAt :becherHouse ;
    ex:owns :starkHydraulicPress ;
    ex:knows :elise ;
    ex:knows :mrFerguson ;
    ex:knows :drBecher ;
    ex:knows :victorHatherley ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
    dc:source :engineersThumbDoc .

