    ex:description "A short, thick man with a chinchilla beard growing out of the creases of his double chin, introduced as Colonel Stark's secretary and manager. He was an Englishman, morose and silent. He was a member of Stark's counterfeiting gang. He appears to have helped Elise carry the unconscious Hatherley to safety (based on unusually large footprints found in the soft mould). He was described as less bold or less murderous than Stark. He fled with the gang before police arrived." ;
    ex:occupation "secretary and manager (cover role)" ;
