    ex:description "An unnamed surpliced clergyman at the Church of St. Monica who officiates the marriage of Irene Adler and Godfrey Norton. Absolutely refused to marry them without a witness, leading to Holmes being dragooned into the role. Beamed on Holmes after the ceremony. Name not given in text." ;
