    ex:description "The unnamed woman for whom John Straker maintained a double life under the alias William Derbyshire. Described by Madame Lesurier as Derbyshire's very dashing wife with a strong partiality for expensive dresses. Her expensive tastes plunged Straker over head and ears in debt, leading him to the plot to disable Silver Blaze. Name not given in the text." ;
    ex:knows :johnStraker, :madameLesurier ;
