:woolwichArsenalWatchman a ex:FictionalPerson ;
    ex:prefLabel "Woolwich Arsenal Watchman" ;
    ex:description "Unnamed watchman at the Arsenal building. An old soldier and a most trustworthy man. Has other departments to look after as well. Saw nothing on Monday evening due to thick fog." ;
