    ex:prefLabel "Saunders" ;
    ex:description "Housemaid at Ridling Thorpe Manor. She was awakened by the sound of explosions at three in the morning. Mrs. King rushed into her room. Together they descended the stairs and found Hilton Cubitt dead and Elsie wounded. She sent for the doctor and constable." ;
    ex:occupation "Housemaid" ;
    ex:employedBy :hiltonCubitt ;
