:136LittleRyderStreetCellar a ex:FictionalLocation, ex:Room ;
    ex:prefLabel "Cellar Under 136 Little Ryder Street" ;
    ex:description "A secret cellar beneath the ground floor of 136 Little Ryder Street, accessed through a trapdoor hidden under the carpet. It housed Rodger Prescott's counterfeiting press, rolls of paper, bottles, and two thousand counterfeit notes. Killer Evans accessed it by pushing the table aside, rolling back the carpet, and using a jemmy to open the floor." ;
