:fulworth a ex:Village ;
    ex:prefLabel "Fulworth" ;
    ex:description "Fulworth is a village on the Sussex coast lying in a hollow curving in a semicircle round a bay. It is an old-fashioned hamlet with several modern houses built upon the rising ground. It has a police station. Tom Bellamy owns the boats and bathing-cots there. The village is near Holmes's retirement villa and The Gables coaching establishment." ;
    ex:locatedIn :sussex, :england, :unitedKingdom ;
    ex:inRegion :sussex ;
    ex:inCountry :unitedKingdom ;
