:rondersWildBeastShow a ex:Organization ;
    ex:prefLabel "Ronder's Wild Beast Show" ;
    ex:description "Ronder's Wild Beast Show is a travelling circus and wild beast exhibition owned by the showman Ronder. It featured the North African lion Sahara King, and employed Leonardo the strong man and Jimmy Griggs the clown, among others. The show was on the down grade as Ronder took to drink, the best men left, and it began to go downhill. The caravan was travelling by road to Wimbledon when the Abbas Parva tragedy occurred." ;
    ex:ownedBy :ronder ;
    ex:employs :eugeniaRonder, :leonardo, :jimmyGriggs ;
    ex:owns :saharaKing ;
