    skos:altLabel "Spencer John crowd" ;
    ex:description "A criminal gang to which Steve Dixie belongs and with which Barney Stockdale is associated. They specialize in assaults, intimidation, and similar dirty work. Holmes has knowledge of them and their activities." ;
