    skos:altLabel "Stimson & Co." ;
    ex:description "Stimson and Co. is an undertaker's business on Kennington Road, London. They were engaged to carry out Rose Spender's funeral, scheduled for eight o'clock in the morning. The shop woman's remark about the coffin being 'out of the ordinary' was the crucial clue in the case." ;
    ex:locatedIn :kenningtonRoad, :london, :england, :unitedKingdom ;
    ex:inCity :london ;
    ex:inStreet :kenningtonRoad ;
    ex:memberOfOntology ex:SherlockOntology ;
