:stockExchange a ex:FinancialInstitution ;
    ex:prefLabel "The Stock Exchange" ;
    skos:altLabel "London Stock Exchange" ;
    ex:description "The Stock Exchange in London. In the Black Peter case, Hopkins examined old Stock Exchange lists for 1883 to identify the initials J.H.N., looking both in the House and among outside brokers, but found no match. Colonel Valentine Walter had a Stock Exchange debt that motivated him to steal the Bruce-Partington plans." ;
    ex:locatedIn :london ;
