    ex:prefLabel "Tankerville Club" ;
    skos:altLabel "the Tankerville" ;
    ex:description "A club in London. Major Prendergast was wrongfully accused of cheating at cards at the Tankerville Club; Sherlock Holmes saved him, and Prendergast later referred John Openshaw to Holmes. Colonel Sebastian Moran was also a member of the club." ;
