:roylottFamily a ex:Organization ;
    ex:prefLabel "Roylotts of Stoke Moran" ;
    skos:altLabel "Roylott family" ;
    ex:description "The Roylotts of Stoke Moran are described as one of the oldest Saxon families in England. Once among the richest in England with estates extending into Berkshire and Hampshire, the family was ruined by four successive dissolute heirs and a gambler in the Regency. Dr. Grimesby Roylott is the last survivor." ;
