:deduction_hisLastBow_holmes_04 a ex:Deduction ;
    ex:prefLabel "Holmes Identifies a Paymaster from Von Bork's Documents" ;
    ex:description "While examining the documents in Von Bork's safe after his capture, Holmes studied a tracing and recognized it as evidence implicating a previously unsuspected paymaster in the spy network." ;
    ex:deductionSequence 4 ;
    ex:deductionSummary "Holmes identified an additional conspirator — a paymaster — by examining a tracing found among Von Bork's papers." ;
    ex:deductionReasoning "Holmes examined a tracing from Von Bork's safe and recognized information that revealed the identity of a paymaster funding the spy ring. Holmes noted he had long had an eye on this individual but had not previously known the full extent of his involvement." ;
    ex:deductionOutcome "correct" ;
    ex:deducedBy :sherlockHolmes ;
    ex:deductionSubject :vonBorkEspionageCampaign ;
