:deduction_redHeadedLeague_holmes_02 a ex:Deduction ;
    ex:prefLabel "Holmes Deduces Wilson Takes Snuff" ;
    ex:description "As part of his initial series of observations about Jabez Wilson, Holmes states that Wilson takes snuff, which Wilson does not dispute." ;
    ex:deductionSequence 2 ;
    ex:deductionSummary "Wilson takes snuff." ;
    ex:deductionReasoning "Holmes observed signs of snuff use on Wilson's person. The reasoning is implied rather than explained, as Holmes declines to insult Wilson's intelligence by spelling it out. Wilson's later use of snuff during the consultation confirms the deduction." ;
    ex:deductionOutcome "correct" ;
    ex:deducedBy :sherlockHolmes ;
    ex:deductionSubject :jabezWilson ;
    ex:confirmedBy :jabezWilson ;
