    ex:deductionSequence 4 ;
    ex:deductionSummary "The murderer is over six feet tall, in the prime of life, and florid-faced" ;
    ex:deductionReasoning "Holmes calculated height from stride length in clay and dust, judged age from the effortless clearing of a wide puddle, and inferred a florid face from the nosebleed blood trail suggesting a robust full-blooded man." ;
